title: Culver City
name: Gaby's Mediterranean Grill
directions: at the intersection with Motor Ave
hours: Open until 1AM on weekdays and 2AM on weekends
content: Reasonably priced and very tasty Lebanese restaurant. Seating is in an outdoor patio complete with hookahs, heat lamps, candles, and a bustling crowd that mixes young hipsters with Lebanese locals. Service is friendly and the place stays busy until closing.
